Rules
-----

1.  Obey the law
2.  Obey staff
3.  Be clean
4.  Be nice
5.  Be honest
6.  No multiplay



Inside the game world, that which is not prohibited by the above is
permitted as far as accounts are concerned.

If you wish to report a violation of the rules, just ring a staffer and
complain.

Please see the topic "rule_X" for information on a specific rule, where
X is the number of the rule.
